Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.37,0:45:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28\fad(150,150)}一個虛幻的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.52,0:45:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28\fad(150,150)}想感受到愛
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.98,0:45:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28\fad(150,150)}那都是幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.90,0:45:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28\fad(150,150)}飄然而至的雪
